<item>
            <title>[DERBY-2243] DatabaseMetaData.supportsANSI92EntryLevelSQL() returns false for embedded, true for client driver</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2243</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since this method is returning the support level of SQL it must be consistent across the drivers.&lt;br/&gt;
Probably need some investigation as to which is correct, most likely &apos;true&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12360554">DERBY-2243</key>
            <summary>DatabaseMetaData.supportsANSI92EntryLevelSQL() returns false for embedded, true for client driver</summary>
